    "description": "揭开次元大陆之谜！<br>『TRANSIRUBY』是一款操作机器人少女Siruby挥剑、开枪打倒敌人不断前进的探索型动作游戏！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737180/extras/Story.png?t=1633007240\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆故事</h2>巨大的次元大陆突如其来的出现。偶然航行在附近宇宙域的机器人少女Siruby和搭档AI「Ne-com」一起奔赴那片次元大陆展开调查……<br><br>次元大陆上有神秘机器人少女「Yamato」、宝藏猎人「Dagurasu」以及众多充满个性的其他角色在等待着Siruby。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737180/extras/Cast.png?t=1633007240\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆游戏特色</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737180/extras/Gimmick.gif?t=1633007240\" /></span><br><br>[神巫女]、[Fairune]的制作者SKIPMORE推出的全新探索型动作游戏！<br>类似[神巫女]的爽快动作加上探索＆解谜要素！<br><br>◎挥剑打倒敌人的爽快感！<br>◎收集金色的菱形Tranchips，打开通往下一个关卡的大门！迷宫追踪游戏・正统机械构造！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737180/extras/Freeze.gif?t=1633007240\" /></span><br><br>◎可以用元素枪冻结敌人并当成「踏板」踩上去！<br>◎适度的谜题和解谜环节，让游戏更加精彩有趣！<br>◎主人公Siruby是机器人，所以也可以变形为摩托车或飞机！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1737180/extras/Transform.gif?t=1633007240\" /></span>",
